1
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:44,270
[A Moment But Forever]

2
00:01:45,060 --> 00:01:47,200
[Episode 12]

3
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:07,750
You're awake.

4
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:13,950
Are you feeling uncomfortable anywhere?

5
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:15,710
No.

6
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:22,460
You were severely injured.

7
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:23,870
It's better for you to rest in bed.

8
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,710
I'm fine now.

9
00:02:32,230 --> 00:02:33,750
This is my friend Mei Shan's residence.

10
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:35,630
He was the one who underwent the lightning tribulation.

11
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:36,910
Lightning tribulation?

12
00:02:42,230 --> 00:02:43,430
Are you alright then?

13
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,590
A tribulation's force is immense

14
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:50,070
and you were sealed away for so long.

15
00:02:50,070 --> 00:02:51,910
Your essence blood has been severely depleted.

16
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,990
How could you disregard yourself

17
00:02:52,990 --> 00:02:54,510
and take on someone else's calamity?

18
00:02:54,829 --> 00:02:55,950
Do you have a death wish?

19
00:02:58,990 --> 00:03:00,150
Apart from creating things,

20
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,550
what other skills do you have?

21
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,510
And how dare you

22
00:03:02,510 --> 00:03:03,670
block a lightning strike for me?

23
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,030
I'm different.

24
00:03:05,230 --> 00:03:06,190
How are you different?

25
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,190
I made a promise

26
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,510
to protect you well.

27
00:03:08,510 --> 00:03:09,390
Of course, I can't let you

28
00:03:09,390 --> 00:03:10,870
lose your life right before my eyes.

29
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:12,110
However,

30
00:03:13,390 --> 00:03:14,310
you need to learn

31
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:15,700
to protect yourself well.

32
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:17,390
I can't save you again.

33
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:19,190
If you encounter such a problem again,

34
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:21,070
I won't be able to intervene.

35
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:23,190
Who did you promise?

36
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,620
When did you promise them?

37
00:03:26,670 --> 00:03:28,280
And why can't you intervene again?

38
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:31,360
I can't tell you.

39
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,150
You...

40
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:37,270
Is this Baitou Mountain?

41
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:39,310
You've been here before?

42
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,380
Yes, I have.

43
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:42,960
But before,

44
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:45,220
this wasn't the name.

45
00:04:09,950 --> 00:04:10,790
Something's not right.

46
00:04:11,790 --> 00:04:12,670
What's not right?

47
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:14,550
I used divination

48
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:16,430
to calculate Tanyin's fortune for this journey.

49
00:04:16,470 --> 00:04:18,310
The result shows it's still a mix of good and bad luck,

50
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,390
unclear and obscure.

51
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:21,350
It's exactly the same as the previous result,

52
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:22,500
with no changes.

53
00:04:22,710 --> 00:04:23,550
How could that be?

54
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,990
Then how do you explain Tanyin's dream?

55
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,340
We are gods.

56
00:04:27,670 --> 00:04:28,680
We don't simply have

57
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,910
insignificant dreams.

58
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,950
What do you think?

59
00:04:32,230 --> 00:04:33,390
Didn't Tanyin say

60
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,550
the High Priest

61
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:36,110
almost killed her in her dream?

62
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,270
Isn't it obvious?

63
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,870
This person stole the Divine Hand

64
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:40,950
and killed countless people.

65
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:42,860
He must have learned Tanyin's identity

66
00:04:42,909 --> 00:04:45,190
and decided to strike first to kill the god and seize the Divine Hand.

67
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,390
It's not impossible.

68
00:04:48,030 --> 00:04:49,480
How can you interpret it

69
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,909
so simplistically and crudely?

70
00:04:50,909 --> 00:04:52,120
In Tanyin's dream,

71
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,860
there was also Deity Taihe.

72
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:55,510
If it's what you said,

73
00:04:55,780 --> 00:04:57,750
then how do you explain Taihe's presence?

74
00:04:58,590 --> 00:04:59,390
Hannv,

75
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:02,430
I know you're worried about Taihe,

76
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,340
but the five Preceptors of Discipline

77
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:05,870
of the Discipline Hall

78
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,630
have already made their decision.

79
00:05:07,670 --> 00:05:10,270
We can only obey.

80
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,650
This... this...

81
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:25,550
May I ask where you're from

82
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:26,810
and which clan you belong to?

83
00:05:28,110 --> 00:05:30,190
I'm from Pingzhou. I'm of the human race.

84
00:05:31,030 --> 00:05:31,820
Pingzhou?

85
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:33,670
Pingzhou...

86
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,870
Are there any... any immortal caves there?

87
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:38,830
Did your ancestors

88
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,440
also have this kind of

89
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,630
talent for resurrection?

90
00:05:46,590 --> 00:05:48,230
I see that you have extraordinary potential

91
00:05:48,230 --> 00:05:49,790
and you're not afraid of the harm from heavenly lightning.

92
00:05:50,150 --> 00:05:52,150
I wonder if you've had any

93
00:05:52,470 --> 00:05:54,190
extraordinary encounters?

94
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:55,630
No, I haven't.

95
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,990
Then, then, then...

96
00:05:59,190 --> 00:05:59,990
Is it

97
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,550
related to the techniques you've practiced?

98
00:06:01,550 --> 00:06:02,940
Can't you ask something useful?

99
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,230
Haven't...

100
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:08,110
Haven't you been suspicious of her all along?

101
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:09,230
I was just asking on your behalf, wasn't I?

102
00:06:09,230 --> 00:06:10,180
Mind your own business.

103
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,910
Hey, you're so ungrateful.

104
00:06:12,030 --> 00:06:13,630
I'm thinking for you.

105
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:14,710
She took

106
00:06:14,710 --> 00:06:15,550
such a big risk for you,

107
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:16,190
suffering the lightning,

108
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:16,950
and saved your life.

109
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:17,910
Yet you're still here,

110
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:18,550
questioning her.

111
00:06:18,550 --> 00:06:19,550
Where are your manners?

112
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:20,550
I didn't ask.

113
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:22,670
You didn't ask?

114
00:06:22,670 --> 00:06:23,590
Even just thinking about it

115
00:06:23,590 --> 00:06:24,630
is impolite.

116
00:06:24,670 --> 00:06:26,110
What's your relationship with her now?

117
00:06:26,110 --> 00:06:27,710
This is a life-and-death relationship.

118
00:06:27,710 --> 00:06:29,390
Yet you keep suspecting her.

119
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:30,550
You're utterly heartless.

120
00:06:30,550 --> 00:06:31,630
Utterly heartless.

121
00:06:31,710 --> 00:06:32,510
Mei Shan,

122
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:34,830
I called you here to check her legs.

123
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,990
If you're not going to treat her,

124
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,390
then get out.

125
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:39,909
Understood, understood.

126
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:54,110
How is it?

127
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,590
Pardon my frankness,

128
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:04,940
but the nerves and muscles in her legs are severely damaged.

129
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:06,550
I'm afraid

130
00:07:07,410 --> 00:07:09,210
there's no possibility of recovery.

131
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:11,710
Even you can't do anything?

132
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:14,300
I can make her a pair of crutches.

133
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,090
Does that count?

134
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:18,750
Don't worry.

135
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:19,750
I'll be fine.

136
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:20,990
It's okay.

137
00:07:21,350 --> 00:07:22,270
If he can't cure you,

138
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,750
I'll find someone else to treat you.

139
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:24,990
There must be a way.

140
00:07:25,790 --> 00:07:26,750
I believe you.

141
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,430
Excuse me, you two,

142
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,390
could you please respect

143
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:31,350
my diagnosis?

144
00:07:31,350 --> 00:07:32,110
If I say

145
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:33,030
these legs can't be cured,

146
00:07:33,030 --> 00:07:33,950
no one can make it happen.

147
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,070
Didn't you say yesterday

148
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:36,510
that if she could come back to life,

149
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:37,710
you'd take off your head

150
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:38,920
and use it as a stool?

151
00:07:38,990 --> 00:07:39,550
Go on.

152
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:40,750
Children should be seen but not heard.

153
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:42,030
If you don't speak, no one will miss you.

154
00:07:42,550 --> 00:07:43,470
Thank you,

155
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,430
but I still prefer to believe

156
00:07:45,430 --> 00:07:46,510
what Yuanzhong said.

157
00:07:47,909 --> 00:07:48,710
Young lady,

158
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,510
I have a question

159
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:52,150
I'd like to discuss with you.

160
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:55,750
This selfless spirit of yours,

161
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:57,860
this noble quality of sacrificing yourself for others,

162
00:07:58,470 --> 00:07:59,909
is it innate

163
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:01,630
or acquired later in life?

164
00:08:02,150 --> 00:08:03,100
To be honest,

165
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,030
I'd like to be friends with you.

166
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,230
The kind that can withstand heavenly thunder for me.

167
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:09,820
Zi Fei.

168
00:08:10,290 --> 00:08:11,800
Young lady, listen to me.

169
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,550
To be frank…

170
00:08:12,590 --> 00:08:13,360
Go, go, go.

171
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:14,620
When I saw your brave act

172
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:15,350
of facing the thunder,

173
00:08:15,350 --> 00:08:16,350
I developed

174
00:08:16,350 --> 00:08:17,550
a deep admiration for you!

175
00:08:17,550 --> 00:08:18,670
Young lady, let's be friends!

176
00:08:18,670 --> 00:08:19,190
Let's go.

177
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:19,550
Young lady!

178
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:20,270
Go out!

179
00:08:20,470 --> 00:08:21,260
Young lady!

180
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,870
That's just how Mei Shan is.

181
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:25,990
He's a bit crazy.

182
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:27,510
Don't take it to heart.

183
00:08:36,850 --> 00:08:39,020
Wh-Why are you staring at me?

184
00:08:42,539 --> 00:08:44,179
I just have a lot of questions I want to ask you.

185
00:08:44,950 --> 00:08:46,070
But I also know

186
00:08:46,590 --> 00:08:47,540
that even if I ask,

187
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:49,490
there won't be any answers.

188
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,030
Are you hungry?

189
00:08:58,470 --> 00:08:59,270
A little.

190
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,310
I'll go get you something to eat.

191
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:17,390
Reporting to the deity,

192
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:19,630
I have dispatched the elites of our clan.

193
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:21,910
We vow to reclaim the God-Slaying Dagger.

194
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:23,610
Please

195
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,710
give my clan one more chance.

196
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,430
You don't even know

197
00:09:27,430 --> 00:09:29,390
if your clansmen are alive or dead.

198
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,190
How will you find them

199
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:32,780
and reclaim the God-Slaying Dagger?

200
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,070
The mortal realm is vast,

201
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:36,320
with countless living beings.

202
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:37,750
With your current

203
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:38,960
manpower and abilities,

204
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,550
trying to find the dagger

205
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:42,300
is like searching for a needle in the haystack.

206
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:44,710
How can I trust you?

207
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:46,140
If I may speak,

208
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:48,310
although our clan is in a difficult situation now,

209
00:09:48,310 --> 00:09:49,710
we are not without allies.

210
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:52,230
I have sent people to contact them

211
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:54,150
and ask for their assistance.

212
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:55,870
There's no time.

213
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:58,030
We must prepare for both possibilities.

214
00:09:58,670 --> 00:10:00,230
I've heard that the War Demon Clan

215
00:10:00,230 --> 00:10:01,350
has a secret technique

216
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:02,630
called Possessing.

217
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:05,150
It's said that if certain conditions are met,

218
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:06,630
one can control someone's body

219
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,100
from thousands of miles away,

220
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:09,550
making them live

221
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:11,070
or die at will.

222
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:12,590
Is this true?

223
00:10:12,870 --> 00:10:13,670
Yes.

224
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,020
What are those necessary conditions

225
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:16,630
that must be met?

226
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,590
War Demons?

227
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:36,830
Do you really want to use them

228
00:10:36,830 --> 00:10:38,900
to perform the possessing technique against Yuanzhong?

229
00:10:39,310 --> 00:10:40,870
If they were capable of succeeding,

230
00:10:41,430 --> 00:10:42,470
they wouldn't have been chased

231
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:43,440
for so many years,

232
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:45,310
unable to see the light of day.

233
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:47,230
I have my own considerations in what I do.

234
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:48,720
There's no need for you to worry.

235
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,470
Still don't feel anything?

236
00:11:35,350 --> 00:11:36,710
But you don't need to worry.

237
00:11:36,780 --> 00:11:38,310
I'm just too badly injured.

238
00:11:38,350 --> 00:11:39,270
It will take some time

239
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,270
to recover.

240
00:11:40,950 --> 00:11:42,110
I'm not worried.

241
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:44,470
It's just that if you don't get better,

242
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:46,350
I don't want to have a cripple

243
00:11:46,350 --> 00:11:47,180
as a handmaiden.

244
00:11:57,860 --> 00:12:00,060
Look, what a nice girl.

245
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,510
Her legs are so badly injured,

246
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:04,590
yet she's still putting on a brave façade.

247
00:12:04,990 --> 00:12:06,510
If I can't be friends with her,

248
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:09,480
it must be against the will of heaven

249
00:12:10,110 --> 00:12:11,240
and I deserve to be struck by lightning.

250
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,630
Are you really trying to

251
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:13,630
befriend her?

252
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,880
I'm almost embarrassed to expose your true intentions.

253
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,630
Why wouldn't I be?

254
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:21,310
Don't doubt my sincerity in making friends.

255
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:23,670
You have ulterior motives.

256
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,440
You just want her to help you bear the lightning.

257
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,660
I don't like what you're saying.

258
00:12:28,660 --> 00:12:29,550
Let me ask you,

259
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,510
when making friends,

260
00:12:30,570 --> 00:12:32,530
shouldn't we be open and honest with each other?

261
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:33,870
When a friend encounters difficulties,

262
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:35,900
shouldn't we be willing to go through thick and thin for them?

263
00:12:36,230 --> 00:12:37,070
In the end,

264
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:37,990
you just want her

265
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:39,190
to help you bear the tribulation.

266
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:41,060
Young man,

267
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:42,750
you need to have a longer-term perspective.

268
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:44,390
If she encounters any difficulties in the future,

269
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:46,390
I will certainly rush to her aid without hesitation.

270
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:47,990
I'd even hold up

271
00:12:47,990 --> 00:12:49,910
the sky for her if it fell, let alone bearing lightning,

272
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:52,950
Anyone can make empty promises.

273
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:54,750
I could even give my life for Yuanzhong.

274
00:13:10,190 --> 00:13:11,110
What are you thinking about?

275
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:22,310
When do you plan to break the seal?

276
00:13:25,430 --> 00:13:26,470
In the next few days.

277
00:13:28,950 --> 00:13:29,910
You're ready?

278
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:34,790
Alright, then in the future,

279
00:13:35,390 --> 00:13:36,150
if there's anything

280
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,310
you need me for,

281
00:13:37,990 --> 00:13:39,070
just let me know.

282
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:40,550
I will.

283
00:13:41,830 --> 00:13:44,390
Can't you show some courtesy?

284
00:13:44,740 --> 00:13:46,020
I did it in my head.

285
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,230
I almost made myself sick.

286
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:58,380
What are

287
00:13:59,030 --> 00:14:00,310
your plans for that girl?

288
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:06,350
