00:28:40,430 --> 00:28:41,750
so it's a bit painful now.

568
00:29:10,910 --> 00:29:11,950
I'm only doing this because

569
00:29:12,190 --> 00:29:13,710
you took a hit for me.

570
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:15,630
Don't overthink it.

571
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:20,830
By the way,

572
00:29:21,310 --> 00:29:22,400
you and Mr. Mei Shan

573
00:29:22,420 --> 00:29:23,540
seem to be good friends.

574
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:24,630
I guess.

575
00:29:24,950 --> 00:29:25,750
Besides me,

576
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:27,550
no one else wants to be his friend.

577
00:29:28,630 --> 00:29:29,750
I heard earlier

578
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:31,190
that you destroyed his cave dwelling

579
00:29:31,270 --> 00:29:32,550
and had a fight with him.

580
00:29:32,990 --> 00:29:33,790
How come

581
00:29:33,830 --> 00:29:35,350
you're now good friends?

582
00:29:36,220 --> 00:29:37,510
Because I showed mercy

583
00:29:37,870 --> 00:29:39,190
and spared his miserable life.

584
00:29:39,350 --> 00:29:41,440
He was grateful to me, worshipped me,

585
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:42,740
and kowtowed to me.

586
00:29:42,740 --> 00:29:43,470
He shamelessly

587
00:29:43,470 --> 00:29:44,590
insisted on being my friend.

588
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:46,310
I had no choice but to give in.

589
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:47,630
I don't believe that.

590
00:29:48,390 --> 00:29:49,750
Having no choice but to give in

591
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:50,710
is actually true.

592
00:29:51,390 --> 00:29:52,310
This guy

593
00:29:52,350 --> 00:29:53,630
is reckless when he goes crazy.

594
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:55,630
But after all, I was in the wrong first.

595
00:29:55,870 --> 00:29:57,150
I destroyed his cave dwelling,

596
00:29:57,230 --> 00:29:59,020
so it wouldn't be right to go all out against him.

597
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:00,750
So you apologized to him?

598
00:30:01,830 --> 00:30:03,440
It was a strategic compromise.

599
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:05,550
What happened after that?

600
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:06,550
After that...

601
00:30:07,870 --> 00:30:09,030
After that, something happened

602
00:30:09,030 --> 00:30:09,990
in the clan.

603
00:30:10,670 --> 00:30:12,430
My Divine Hand power was sealed.

604
00:30:12,830 --> 00:30:14,030
Kai Shan and the others

605
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:15,710
were also sealed in different places.

606
00:30:16,710 --> 00:30:17,550
This Baitou Mountain

607
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:19,110
is where Kai Shan is sealed.

608
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,430
After that,

609
00:30:20,910 --> 00:30:23,310
Mei Shan helped me guard this place.

610
00:30:28,510 --> 00:30:29,310
Does it hurt?

611
00:30:30,190 --> 00:30:30,980
A little bit.

612
00:30:31,870 --> 00:30:33,980
Bear with it. It helps with recovery.

613
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:00,960
Why are you looking at me?

614
00:31:02,390 --> 00:31:03,190
It's nothing.

615
00:31:03,630 --> 00:31:04,820
Am I not massaging well?

616
00:31:05,260 --> 00:31:06,110
It's fine.

617
00:31:06,840 --> 00:31:09,070
Just feels a bit tingly.

618
00:31:16,220 --> 00:31:18,180
That means it's almost healed.

619
00:31:19,780 --> 00:31:21,540
That's enough for today.

620
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,350
You should rest now.

621
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:42,710
Please.

622
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:46,950
Esteemed guest,

623
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:49,630
are you satisfied with this fish?

624
00:31:50,150 --> 00:31:51,110
Thank you, waiter.

625
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,190
You're welcome, you're welcome.

626
00:31:52,190 --> 00:31:53,500
Enjoy your meal.

627
00:31:55,350 --> 00:31:56,670
This is bream from the Min River.

628
00:31:56,950 --> 00:31:58,150
The taste is exquisite.

629
00:31:58,470 --> 00:31:59,710
If we hadn't passed by here,

630
00:31:59,750 --> 00:32:01,230
we wouldn't have had such a delicacy.

631
00:32:02,060 --> 00:32:03,950
We're just passing acquaintances, Sir.

632
00:32:04,590 --> 00:32:06,150
I don't know why

633
00:32:06,170 --> 00:32:07,200
you've invited me here.

634
00:32:07,670 --> 00:32:09,390
We're not just passing acquaintances.

635
00:32:10,200 --> 00:32:11,230
Although it's a bit late,

636
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:12,630
I still remembered you.

637
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:25,830
This is liquor from the Min River.

638
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:26,950
Though not a fine wine,

639
00:32:27,340 --> 00:32:28,790
it has its own unique flavor.

640
00:32:31,710 --> 00:32:32,510
Please.

641
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:44,590
How does it taste?

642
00:32:50,710 --> 00:32:52,350
When did you remember me?

643
00:32:53,150 --> 00:32:54,990
You felt familiar when I first saw you.

644
00:32:55,590 --> 00:32:56,710
After thinking carefully,

645
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,260
I remembered.

646
00:32:59,340 --> 00:33:00,920
Do you have something to tell me?

647
00:33:03,250 --> 00:33:05,040
This sword is quite special.

648
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:06,340
The blade is a bit shorter.

649
00:33:06,570 --> 00:33:07,890
The hilt is also thinner.

650
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,410
May I take a look?

651
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,550
The hilt fits well in my hand.

652
00:33:34,550 --> 00:33:35,830
The blade is sharp enough too.

653
00:33:36,690 --> 00:33:37,600
It's a good sword.

654
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,090
Does this sword have a name?

655
00:33:41,260 --> 00:33:42,350
You don't recognize it?

656
00:33:43,190 --> 00:33:44,470
Should I recognize it?

657
00:33:45,190 --> 00:33:45,920
Then why

658
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,350
did you say you recognized me?

659
00:33:49,150 --> 00:33:50,670
You're a handmaiden from Xiaoxiang Peak.

660
00:33:51,470 --> 00:33:52,230
When I was confined by the Elders

661
00:33:52,230 --> 00:33:53,470
in Jinxia Palace,

662
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:55,130
you came to clean the room.

663
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,590
What? Did I remember wrong?

664
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:07,920
No.

665
00:34:08,830 --> 00:34:09,989
You remembered correctly, Sir.

666
00:34:10,389 --> 00:34:12,270
I was indeed a handmaiden from Xiaoxiang Peak.

667
00:34:12,650 --> 00:34:14,159
We've met a few times.

668
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:16,270
My status is humble.

669
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:17,800
I'm flattered that you remember.

670
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,340
Don't worry.

671
00:34:19,949 --> 00:34:20,870
Over these decades,

672
00:34:21,190 --> 00:34:22,670
it's not unheard of for human handmaidens

673
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:24,030
to quietly slip away.

674
00:34:24,670 --> 00:34:25,429
I've come down the mountain this time

675
00:34:25,429 --> 00:34:26,670
for other important matters to attend to.

676
00:34:26,790 --> 00:34:27,840
I won't give you any trouble.

677
00:34:29,929 --> 00:34:31,050
You're so generous.

678
00:34:31,739 --> 00:34:33,139
Thank you so much, Sir.

679
00:34:33,750 --> 00:34:34,880
Judging by your physique,

680
00:34:35,350 --> 00:34:36,590
you must be trained in martial arts.

681
00:34:37,790 --> 00:34:39,030
Did you learn it before coming to the mountain?

682
00:34:41,389 --> 00:34:44,030
As a human, my status is lowly.

683
00:34:44,699 --> 00:34:45,530
Would anyone

684
00:34:45,679 --> 00:34:47,090
from Fangwai Mountain teach me martial arts there?

685
00:34:48,830 --> 00:34:49,750
Perhaps you think

686
00:34:49,750 --> 00:34:51,010
I learned it secretly?

687
00:34:51,750 --> 00:34:53,360
You seem to dislike me.

688
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:54,540
I wouldn't dare.

689
00:34:56,909 --> 00:34:58,070
I'm just curious.

690
00:34:58,670 --> 00:35:00,310
Since you're trained in martial arts,

691
00:35:00,990 --> 00:35:02,550
why did you go to the mountain as a handmaiden?

692
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:08,910
If you don't want to,

693
00:35:09,110 --> 00:35:10,070
you don't have to tell me.

694
00:35:10,470 --> 00:35:11,870
I'm just curious, that's all.

695
00:35:13,950 --> 00:35:15,350
I was looking for an answer.

696
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:17,390
An answer?

697
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:19,550
When I was young,

698
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:21,390
I accidentally entered a spiritual mountain.

699
00:35:22,540 --> 00:35:24,020
All traces of life had vanished on the mountain.

700
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,230
There was only the light of snow everywhere,

701
00:35:26,430 --> 00:35:27,830
as if blessed by the gods.

702
00:35:29,070 --> 00:35:29,870
I...

703
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:33,350
I encountered a deer.

704
00:35:34,140 --> 00:35:35,420
It stood majestically

705
00:35:35,450 --> 00:35:36,770
in the wind and snow.

706
00:35:37,610 --> 00:35:38,730
I looked into its eyes

707
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:40,740
and felt

708
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:42,500
an unprecedented stirring in my heart.

709
00:35:43,710 --> 00:35:45,190
It was as if it were

710
00:35:45,750 --> 00:35:46,990
the only color in the world.

711
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:49,100
I thought at the time

712
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:50,990
that all things have spirits

713
00:35:51,580 --> 00:35:53,230
and our meeting was no coincidence.

714
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:54,910
For many years after that,

715
00:35:55,310 --> 00:35:57,550
I searched for this deer.

716
00:35:58,350 --> 00:35:59,190
I heard

717
00:35:59,630 --> 00:36:01,390
it was a divine deer from the spiritual mountain.

718
00:36:01,970 --> 00:36:03,040
It was extremely rare.

719
00:36:03,580 --> 00:36:04,380
Perhaps...

720
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:11,870
Perhaps something belonging to the divine race

721
00:36:11,870 --> 00:36:13,070
might be on Fangwai Mountain.

722
00:36:14,150 --> 00:36:15,390
I went up the mountain to serve as a handmaiden

723
00:36:16,110 --> 00:36:18,060
and searched for it for many years.

724
00:36:18,790 --> 00:36:19,870
Did you find it?

725
00:36:22,310 --> 00:36:24,190
Later, I did indeed see it again.

726
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,300
Isn't that good?

727
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:28,580
It's both good and not so good, I suppose.

728
00:36:31,870 --> 00:36:33,390
Its appearance hadn't changed,

729
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,440
but it was completely different

730
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:37,540
from the clear and transparent,

731
00:36:37,790 --> 00:36:38,830
ethereal,

732
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:41,220
almost otherworldly feeling

733
00:36:41,250 --> 00:36:42,420
I remembered.

734
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,710
So you were disappointed?

735
00:36:45,950 --> 00:36:47,310
I wouldn't say disappointed.

736
00:36:57,430 --> 00:36:58,830
So many years have passed.

737
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:01,310
I can barely remember

738
00:37:01,590 --> 00:37:03,070
what it originally looked like.

739
00:37:04,230 --> 00:37:05,260
It was nothing more than

740
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,550
an illusion

741
00:37:06,870 --> 00:37:07,870
that I had beautified

742
00:37:07,870 --> 00:37:08,950
many times in my mind.

743
00:37:09,390 --> 00:37:10,790
To judge the present version

744
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:12,150
against an imagined one

745
00:37:12,350 --> 00:37:13,710
isn't fair to him.

746
00:37:15,430 --> 00:37:16,190
Perhaps the one I met

747
00:37:16,190 --> 00:37:17,280
back then

748
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:19,230
wasn't his true self to begin with,

749
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:20,950
but rather who I thought he was.

750
00:37:21,750 --> 00:37:22,590
Moreover,

751
00:37:25,310 --> 00:37:26,870
he had long forgotten about me.

752
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,350
You seem to have deep insights.

753
00:37:30,830 --> 00:37:31,950
Not exactly.

754
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:35,190
I've been trapped in my obsession for too many years.

755
00:37:35,470 --> 00:37:37,060
It's time to let go.

756
00:37:38,790 --> 00:37:39,720
How old are you?

757
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:42,150
You're too young to talk about "too many years."

758
00:37:43,030 --> 00:37:44,070
But that's good.

759
00:37:44,990 --> 00:37:46,740
Wasting your life for a deer

760
00:37:47,450 --> 00:37:48,510
is truly unwise.

761
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:51,430
You're right to admonish me, Sir.

762
00:37:58,010 --> 00:38:00,160
This sword seems destined for you, Sir.

763
00:38:01,990 --> 00:38:03,170
Please accept it as a gift.

764
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:06,700
♫I gaze into your deep eyes♫

765
00:38:04,430 --> 00:38:05,340
What do you mean?

766
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:11,380
♫For whom do you take apart the word "love"?♫

767
00:38:08,590 --> 00:38:10,180
Consider it a thank you for the wine you offered.

768
00:38:13,780 --> 00:38:17,420
♫Turning around, it's like a dream♫

769
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:22,380
♫I have betrayed deep love♫

770
00:38:23,790 --> 00:38:27,880
♫Unable to get what I yearn for, I sink in sadness♫

771
00:38:29,410 --> 00:38:33,650
♫When I brush past love fate is set♫

772
00:38:34,410 --> 00:38:37,010
♫I've used up my brush and ink♫

773
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:40,330
♫But I can't describe♫

774
00:38:40,500 --> 00:38:45,060
♫This lovesick path♫

775
00:38:57,780 --> 00:38:58,810
Kai Shan is right here.

776
00:38:59,140 --> 00:38:59,990
So you're saying

777
00:39:00,260 --> 00:39:01,030
he sealed himself

778
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:02,680
in the hot spring?

779
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:04,590
He found a good place, right?

780
00:39:06,170 --> 00:39:07,810
According to what the Divine Hand has detected,

781
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:09,030
he's in an even deeper place

782
00:39:09,030 --> 00:39:10,030
below the hot spring.

783
00:39:10,310 --> 00:39:11,950
It's surrounded by scorching energy.

784
00:39:12,830 --> 00:39:14,580
What should we do? Let's fish him out.

785
00:39:21,220 --> 00:39:22,870
Kai Shan, return.

786
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,630
Yuanzhong, up there.

787
00:39:46,220 --> 00:39:47,910
Tell me about the restrictions on this mountain

788
00:39:47,930 --> 00:39:49,290
and its original owner.

789
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:52,030
Well, you're asking the wrong person.

790
00:39:52,230 --> 00:39:53,310
It's my first time seeing

791
00:39:53,310 --> 00:39:54,230
the full extent of the restrictions.

792
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:55,020
As for this place

793
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:56,630
and its former owner,

794
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:58,230
I've never even met him.

795
00:40:00,830 --> 00:40:01,630
That's not right.

796
00:40:02,590 --> 00:40:03,270
This person set up

797
00:40:03,270 --> 00:40:04,670
such extensive restrictions.

798
00:40:04,990 --> 00:40:06,790
He couldn't have done it overnight.

799
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:08,870
Surely their intention

800
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:10,790
was to maintain the mountain's appearance

801
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:12,390
and prevent others from damaging

802
00:40:12,390 --> 00:40:13,760
even a blade of grass and leaf on this mountain.

803
00:40:14,270 --> 00:40:15,190
How could he allow you

804
00:40:15,190 --> 00:40:16,550
to leisurely undergo your tribulations here?

805
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,030
Well, if you put it that way,

806
00:40:20,040 --> 00:40:21,760
there is indeed something strange.

807
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,710
When I first arrived here,

808
00:40:23,710 --> 00:40:24,540
there was always this old fellow

809
00:40:24,540 --> 00:40:25,390
who came to give me trouble

810
00:40:25,390 --> 00:40:26,390
and tried to drive me away.

811
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:27,390
And then?

812
00:40:27,830 --> 00:40:28,750
Then I fought with him

813
00:40:28,750 --> 00:40:29,430
for several years.

814
00:40:29,430 --> 00:40:30,430
When he saw he couldn't do anything about me,

815
00:40:30,430 --> 00:40:31,590
he never came back.

816
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:35,350
Divine artifacts have spirits.

817
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:36,710
They wouldn't choose

818
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:37,990
to seal themselves here without reason.

819
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:39,950
Could it be because

820
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:41,110
this place has restrictions

821
00:40:41,220 --> 00:40:42,020
that it's

822
00:40:42,020 --> 00:40:43,150
the safest for him?

823
00:40:43,780 --> 00:40:45,460
But the problem is it's too safe.

824
00:40:45,740 --> 00:40:47,140
Even I can't do anything about it.

825
00:40:49,750 --> 00:40:50,670
Don't tell me

826
00:40:50,670 --> 00:40:52,230
that you, the mighty host of the Divine Hand,

827
00:40:52,230 --> 00:40:52,910
can't break

828
00:40:52,910 --> 00:40:54,110
the restrictions here.

829
00:40:56,940 --> 00:40:58,060
You really can't break them?

830
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,630
Forget about breaking the restrictions.

831
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:02,390
I just tried to deduce it,

832
00:41:02,670 --> 00:41:03,630
but I couldn't even determine

833
00:41:03,630 --> 00:41:04,700
the direction of the formation's eye.

834
00:41:06,910 --> 00:41:08,000
What should we do then?

835
00:41:18,870 --> 00:41:20,510
Take care, Sir. Please come again.

836
00:41:23,990 --> 00:41:25,030
The Juque Sword?

837
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:28,470
What did you say?

838
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,440
This is the Juque Sword?

839
00:41:33,030 --> 00:41:33,830
Sir, you don't

840
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:35,100
recognize this sword?

841
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:37,070
It is said that this sword

842
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:38,500
was the fifth sword

843
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,470
forged by Ouye Zi.

844
00:41:39,830 --> 00:41:40,710
On the day it was completed,

845
00:41:40,710 --> 00:41:42,590
its aura pierced the sky, emitting a brilliant light.

846
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:44,760
Today, I've truly seen something great.

847
00:41:45,110 --> 00:41:46,620
Are you sure this is the Juque Sword?

848
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,710
I specifically searched for this sword in the past.

849
00:41:48,740 --> 00:41:49,750
The Juque Sword in the sword diagram

850
00:41:49,750 --> 00:41:50,990
doesn't look like this.

