00:41:51,030 --> 00:41:52,070
You said it yourself.

852
00:41:52,070 --> 00:41:53,070
It's just a diagram.

853
00:41:53,230 --> 00:41:54,190
After so many years,

854
00:41:54,220 --> 00:41:55,270
people have passed on inaccurate information,

855
00:41:55,270 --> 00:41:56,470
drawing based on imagination.

856
00:41:56,830 --> 00:41:58,110
It can't be very accurate.

857
00:41:58,580 --> 00:42:00,140
Now, you have obtained the precious sword,

858
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:01,810
yet you fail to recognize it.

859
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:02,640
This is truly...

860
00:42:09,580 --> 00:42:10,580
I came out this time

861
00:42:11,010 --> 00:42:12,260
just to find it.

862
00:42:12,670 --> 00:42:13,830
Since you want to find it,

863
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,430
I will surely find it for you.

864
00:42:17,890 --> 00:42:18,680
Innkeeper,

865
00:42:18,870 --> 00:42:19,590
where is the young lady

866
00:42:19,590 --> 00:42:20,550
who dined with me yesterday?

867
00:42:21,390 --> 00:42:22,110
That young lady

868
00:42:22,110 --> 00:42:23,750
checked out and left early this morning.

869
00:42:24,070 --> 00:42:24,870
She left?

870
00:42:25,290 --> 00:42:26,460
Do you know where she went?

871
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:28,600
I have no idea about that.

872
00:42:32,010 --> 00:42:34,290
Are all these for me?

873
00:42:34,580 --> 00:42:36,060
Yes, they're all for you.

874
00:42:38,510 --> 00:42:39,880
They look quite nice.

875
00:42:39,950 --> 00:42:41,200
They're not just nice-looking.

876
00:42:41,350 --> 00:42:42,470
If you wind it up,

877
00:42:42,470 --> 00:42:43,510
it can even move.

878
00:42:43,530 --> 00:42:44,330
Give it a try.

879
00:42:52,670 --> 00:42:54,150
Can I ask you a favor?

880
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:54,910
Go ahead.

881
00:42:55,110 --> 00:42:56,070
Can you go down the mountain

882
00:42:56,070 --> 00:42:57,350
and buy a roast goose for me?

883
00:42:57,950 --> 00:42:59,240
No problem. Just wait here.

884
00:43:00,350 --> 00:43:01,060
Thanks.

885
00:43:01,090 --> 00:43:01,890
No problem.
